      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Automated review compliance release.\n\n- minAppVersion is now 1.8.7: sidebar preferences persist via App#saveLocalStorage / App#loadLocalStorage, vault lookups via getFileByPath.\n- moment removed from plugin code in favor of native Date helpers.\n- Promise and type hygiene across the codebase; dead code deleted; docs site moved to the docs branch.\n- Release assets (main.js, styles.css, manifest.json) now carry GitHub artifact attestations, and the build reproduces byte-for-byte from source.\n",
