      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Smart Gantt is back, rebuilt.\n\n## Highlights\n\n- Bespoke gantt engine: drag a bar to reschedule and the date is rewritten in your note, resize edges, Day/Week/Month/Quarter zoom, today line, weekend shading.\n- Understands dates in plain language (\"due next monday\", \"tomorrow\"), Tasks-style emoji dates, and Dataview `[due:: ]` fields - no special syntax required.\n- Premium UI overhaul: design tokens derived from your Obsidian theme so every community theme harmonizes, one floating glass toolbar per view, reduced-motion support.\n- Sidebar auto-refreshes when notes change.\n- Settings migrated to Obsidian loadData/saveData with one-time automatic import.\n- Legacy mermaid/marked/CodeMirror 5 paths removed; bundle down from 2.45 MB to 1.82 MB.\n\n![sidebar](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nhannht/obsidian-smart-gantt/0.2.0/showcase/sidebar-dark.png)\n",
      "downloadCount": 2,
